body_html: @yaroslavvb the hex address shows up when the symbol lookup failed. Address to symbol name mappings are always very brittle. You can try to fiddle with build options to see if it helps. You need the frame pointers for instance, IIRC. If you gdb attach to it, then info symbol, then you might be able to reverse map it.
